data.title: WHERE LATE THE SWEET BIRDS SANG
data.meta_description: New York: Harper & Row, Publishers, 1976 . First edition. Hugo Award winner. SIGNED ON BOOKPLATE affixed to front endpaper. Bright and near fine with just a small bump to upper front board; in a supplied, bright, crisp, and near fine dust jacket with small tear and touch of rubbing to upper front corner internally mended with tiny piece of archival tape . Scarce. Item #71944
